@startuml Axora Processing Pipeline States

title Axora Query and URL Processing State Transitions

' Query Processing States
state QCreated as "Query Created"
state QSearching as "Search Processing"
state QProcessing as "Background Processing"
state QCompleted as "Query Completed"
state QFailed as "Query Failed"

[*] --> QCreated : User submits query
QCreated --> QSearching : Search module starts
QSearching --> QProcessing : URLs found & stored
QSearching --> QFailed : Search API error
QProcessing --> QCompleted : All URLs processed
QProcessing --> QFailed : Critical processing error
QFailed --> [*]
QCompleted --> [*]

note right of QProcessing
    Query stays in processing while
    URLs are being scraped, crawled,
    and analyzed in background
end note

' URL Processing States
state UDiscovered as "URL Discovered"
state UScraping as "Content Scraping"
state UScraped as "Content Scraped"
state UCrawling as "Crawling Links"
state UCrawled as "Links Crawled"
state UCompleted as "URL Completed"
state UFailed as "URL Failed"

UDiscovered --> UScraping : Scraper picks up URL
UScraping --> UScraped : Content extracted successfully
UScraping --> UFailed : HTTP error, timeout,\nor parsing failure
UScraped --> UCrawling : Crawler starts link discovery
UCrawling --> UCrawled : New URLs discovered & stored
UCrawling --> UFailed : Robots.txt violation\nor crawl depth exceeded
UCrawled --> UCompleted : Processing complete

note right of UCrawling
    Crawler respects robots.txt
    and depth limits (default: 2)
    Creates new URL records
    with incremented depth_level
end note


' Error Handling & Retry Logic
state RetryQueue as "Retry Queue"
state MaxRetries as "Max Retries Reached"

UFailed --> RetryQueue : Retryable error\n(network, timeout)
RetryQueue --> UScraping : Retry attempt
RetryQueue --> MaxRetries : Max retries exceeded

note right of RetryQueue
    Configurable retry logic:
    - Network timeouts
    - HTTP 5xx errors
    - Rate limiting
    
    Non-retryable errors:
    - HTTP 4xx errors
    - Content parsing failures
    - Robots.txt violations
end note

' Cross-package relationships
QProcessing --> UDiscovered : Creates URL processing jobs
UCompleted --> QProcessing : Contributes to query completion
UFailed --> QProcessing : May affect query status

@enduml